                      Extract the key points into categories:
                      1. Threats (intimidation, bans, police cases)
                      2. Admissions (employer admits they owe money or haven't paid)
                      3. Promises (employer promises to pay on X date)
                      4. Inconsistencies (dates don't match, amounts differ from contract)
                      5. Red Flags (illegal clauses, asking to sign before payment)

                      Summarize the document content briefly.` 
