                - User Description: "${description}"

                TASK:
                1. Identify the specific jurisdiction (MOHRE Mainland, DMCC, JAFZA, DIFC, etc) and customize the "Next Steps".
                2. Assess risk. "High" if there is coercion, passport holding, fake absconding, or amount > 50k AED unpaid.
                3. Create a strict list of DOs and DONTs.
                4. **CRITICAL**: Provide exact contact details for the authority (Phone, Email) from the database.
                5. **CRITICAL**: Draft a formal inquiry email that the user can send to the Authority.
                6. **CRITICAL (Strategic Questions)**: Generate 3-4 specific, hard-hitting questions the employee should ask the employer to demand proof or expose lies.
                7. **CRITICAL (Roadmap)**: Generate a step-by-step To-Do list (Roadmap) for the user to resolve this issue.
                   - 'Document': Tasks like 'Find Offer Letter', 'Download Bank Statement'.
                   - 'Action': Tasks like 'Calculate End of Service', 'Send Inquiry Email'.
                   - 'Official': Tasks like 'Register Complaint on MOHRE App', 'Attend Mediation'.
                   - Limit to 5-7 most important steps.

                OUTPUT REQUIREMENT:
                - Respond strictly in ${lang} language.
                - JSON format only.
              `,
              config: {
                  responseMimeType: 'application/json',
                  responseSchema: {
                      type: Type.OBJECT,
                      properties: {
                          diagnosis: { type: Type.STRING },
                          risk: { type: Type.STRING, enum: ['Low', 'Medium', 'High'] },
                          dos: { type: Type.ARRAY, items: { type: Type.STRING } },
                          donts: { type: Type.ARRAY, items: { type: Type.STRING } },
                          strategicQuestions: { type: Type.ARRAY, items: { type: Type.STRING } },
                          authorityContact: {
                              type: Type.OBJECT,
                              properties: {
                                  name: { type: Type.STRING },
                                  phone: { type: Type.STRING },
                                  email: { type: Type.STRING },
                                  portal: { type: Type.STRING }
                              }
                          },
                          suggestedEmail: {
                              type: Type.OBJECT,
                              properties: {
                                  subject: { type: Type.STRING },
                                  body: { type: Type.STRING }
                              }
                          },
                          roadmap: {
                              type: Type.ARRAY,
                              items: {
                                  type: Type.OBJECT,
                                  properties: {
                                      title: { type: Type.STRING },
                                      description: { type: Type.STRING },
                                      category: { type: Type.STRING, enum: ['Document', 'Action', 'Official'] }
                                  }
                              }
                          }
                      }
                  }
              }
          });
          if (response.text) {
              return JSON.parse(response.text);
          }
      } catch (e) {
          console.warn("Gemini API call failed, falling back to mock.", e);
      }
  }

  // Improved Fallback Mock Logic
  await new Promise(resolve => setTimeout(resolve, 1500)); 

  const isFreezone = employerType === 'Freezone';
  const specificAuth = freezone || 'Freezone Authority';

  const mockDos = [
      "Keep a copy of all WhatsApp/Email proofs.",
      "Calculate your exact gratuity and unpaid salary.",
      isFreezone 
        ? `Log into the ${specificAuth} portal and search for 'Labour Dispute'.`
        : "Download the MOHRE App and select 'Register Labour Complaint'."
  ];

  const mockDonts = [
      "DO NOT sign the visa cancellation paper if you haven't received cash/transfer.",
      "DO NOT resign if they are forcing you (unless you cite Article 45 for non-payment).",
      "DO NOT accept a cheque as final settlement (high risk of bouncing)."
  ];

  const mockQuestions = [
      "If you state payment has been made, please provide the WPS Reference Number.",
      "Please confirm in writing (email) exactly when the End of Service Benefits will be released.",
      "Can you provide a breakdown of the deduction you are mentioning?"
  ];

  return {
    diagnosis: `${getMockResponseText(lang, 'diagnosis')} (${issues.join(", ")})`,
    risk: "Medium",
    dos: mockDos,
    donts: mockDonts,
    strategicQuestions: mockQuestions,
    authorityContact: {
        name: isFreezone ? specificAuth : "MOHRE",
        phone: isFreezone ? "See Freezone Website" : "600590000",
        email: isFreezone ? "info@freezone.ae" : "ask@mohre.gov.ae",
        portal: isFreezone ? "Portal" : "MOHRE App"
    },
    suggestedEmail: {
        subject: "Urgent: Labour Dispute Inquiry",
        body: "To whom it may concern,\n\nI am writing to file a formal complaint regarding unpaid salary..."
    },
    roadmap: [
        { title: "Collect Documents", description: "Gather contract, visa copy, and bank statements.", category: "Document" },
        { title: "Calculate Dues", description: "Use the Gratuity Calculator to know your rights.", category: "Action" },
        { title: "Contact Employer", description: "Send the formal inquiry email.", category: "Action" },
        { title: "File Complaint", description: `Register case with ${isFreezone ? specificAuth : 'MOHRE'}.`, category: "Official" }
